About Me

Who Am I?

My name is Viet Anh or you can call me Viet (it is shorter and easier to pronounce and remember :p){" "}

I am a master information science student from University of Apllied Science Darmstadt, Germany. I love make things pretty, photograph.

I write faster than i think, so please let me know if I wrote something wrong :D

What can I do?

Here are some of my knowlegdes and skills

Language

English, German, Vietnamese (mother-tongue language)

EDV

MS Office (sehr gute Kenntnisse in Word, PowerPoint, gute Kenntnisse in Excel), LaTeX

IT-Knowlegde

HTML, CSS, PHP, JavaScript, ReactJS, MySQL, D3, Python, XML GraphDB, Protégé, Lodview, Karma
